ost/%D9%85%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%87%DB%8C%D9%85_%D9%88_%D8%AE%D8%B5%D9%88%D8%B5%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA_%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3%DB%8C%D9%82%DB%8C_%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C_%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF%DB%8C%E2%80%8C%D9%81%D8%B1_%DB%8C%DA%A9%D8%B4%D9%86%D8%A8%D9%87_30_%D8%AE%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AF|accessdate=22 October 2016}}</ref> * [[Aleatory Music]] <ref name="Contemporary Music"/> * Musical Terms <ref name="Contemporary Music"/> * Nonserial Atonality Music <ref name="Contemporary Music"/> * Neo Romanticism <ref name="Contemporary Music"/> * Classical Serialism and Total Serialism <ref name="Contemporary Music"/> * Analysis of Bach's Chromatic Fantasia and Fugue <ref>{{cite web|last1=Ahmadifar|first1=Ali|title=Analysis of Bach's Chromatic Fantasia and Fugue|url=http://kfgil.com/Post/%D8%A2%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B2_%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%B2%DB%8C_%DA%A9%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%AA%DB%8C%DA%A9_%D9%88_%D9%81%D9%88%DA%AF_%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AE_%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C_%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF%DB%8C%E2%80%8C%D9%81%D8%B1_%D8%B3%D9%87%E2%80%8C%D8%B4%D9%86%D8%A8%D9%87_29_%D8%AA%DB%8C%D8%B1|accessdate=22 October 2016}}</ref> * [[Steve Reich]] * [[Philip Glass]] * [[Arvo Pärt]] * [[Contemporary music]] * Iranian composers * Pathology of Iranian today music<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ahmadifar|first1=Ali|title=Pathology of Iranian today music Lecture|url=http://www.kfgil.com/Post/%D8%A2%D8%B3%DB%8C%D8%A8%E2%80%8C%E2%80%8C%D8%B4%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%B3%DB%8C_%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3%DB%8C%D9%82%DB%8C_%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B2_%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86__%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C_%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF%DB%8C%E2%80%8C%D9%81%D8%B1__9_%D8%AE%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AF|website=www.kfgil.com|accessdate=12 December 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222074638/http://www.kfgil.com/Post/%D8%A2%D8%B3%DB%8C%D8%A8%E2%80%8C%E2%80%8C%D8%B4%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%B3%DB%8C_%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3%DB%8C%D9%82%DB%8C_%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B2_%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86__%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C_%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF%DB%8C%E2%80%